{"tid":2315353,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［醒目啲］中大遊行係徹頭徹尾嘅送頭行動，根本就係撩鬼攞命！","createTime":"2020-12-07T06:43:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T10:03:50.000Z","uid":219007,"like":44,"dislike":441,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"9b172eac77da07455429756e61f2138b726d6a65","tid":2315353,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T06:43:30.000Z","msg":"無論你哋聽唔聽得入耳，我都係咁話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家咩時勢大佬，社運低潮、萬馬齊喑<br />\n<br />\n你班細路無啦啦衝出嚟遊行？ 仲要喺鏡頭前面叫禁語口號，咁樣同叫人嚟拉你有咩分別？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係想抗爭嘅話都要等下先，更何況而家沖出嚟做呢啲嘢一定死硬。 <br />\n<br />\n依家走又唔係，唔走又唔係。 比着我就趁個學位仲有價值嘅時候Lele Lala 拎埋張沙紙就去英國5+1過新生活好過，起碼唔使喺香港受苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n拎個計數機出嚟篤下就知邊條路着數<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n醒目啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4d89660f6921f7d6ba8e282f1672177865411d9","tid":2315353,"uid":310914,"like":6,"dislike":26,"score":-20,"quote":{"pid":"9b172eac77da07455429756e61f2138b726d6a65","tid":2315353,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T06:43:30.000Z","msg":"無論你哋聽唔聽得入耳，我都係咁話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fa